Installation

	Please read the INSTALL file for installation instructions.

Testing

	After installing the SVIS Toolbox, you may run the test file,
	
        >> svistest

	from the MATLAB command prompt to test the software.

Benchmarking

	To get an idea of how the SVIS Toolbox functions perform on your
	particular platform, you may run the benchmark program,

        >> svisbenchmark

	from the MATLAB command prompt.

Examples

	The SVIS Toolbox 'examples' directory contains example programs
	that illustrate SVIS Toolbox function usage.
